data.description: THIS INCLUDES THE 10 ACRES BEHIND THE HOME IN ADDITION TO THE 10 WITH THE HOME FOR A 20 ACRE PARCEL ALL TOGETHER!!!! VERY RARE OPPORTUNITY! ONCE IN A LIFETIME IS A HOME/WORKING ESTABLISHMENT OF THIS CALIBER IS OFFERED!20 Beautiful acres! Open concept Saltwater pool home features 12 ft coffered ceilings, travertine floors, a split floor plan and sliders right out to the pool with a swim up bar and over sized covered patio. The Custom kitchen has granite counter tops. custom cabinetry with glass doors, gas stove and a breakfast bar 2nd to none! The absolute beauty that surrounds you from the Private iron gate to the 2 acre stocked pond with water fountain is just a taste of what this exquisite compound has to offer. Have BOATS? RV'S? MULTIPLE CARS TO WORK ON? THIS business property can do it all! In addition to the 4 car garage, you have your own fueling station, a custom reverse osmosis water filtration system that runs the entire property, 2 Complete RV hook ups, a hot rod shop with lifts all the way up to RV's or Semi Trucks, Air Conditioned bays and a complete office with conference room, full bath and Kitchen. There are endless possibilities. MUST SEE TO APPRECIATE EVERYTHING THIS WORKING PROPERTY HAS TO OFFER!
